the msk cluster should create a role that allows to read/write to the cluster `kafka-cluster:*`.
the created role should be assumed in your kafka connector this way: 

    {
      &quot;Effect&quot;: &quot;Allow&quot;,
      &quot;Action&quot;: &quot;iam:PassRole&quot;,
      &quot;Resource&quot;: &quot;*&quot;
    }
and then, add to this policy the operation that you want to do with the kafka cluster: 

    {
      &quot;Effect&quot;: &quot;Allow&quot;,
      &quot;Action&quot;: &quot;kafka-cluster:*&quot;,
      &quot;Resource&quot;: &quot;*&quot;
    }

hope that help you

